{"tid":2248513,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本GV天菜沖修斗 圓夢與偶像G星合作對手戲出道","createTime":"2020-10-18T15:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T15:00:50.000Z","uid":3189,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"17bd16db7ca92947f69f45a7cb7de9776f28cb6f","tid":2248513,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:54:10.000Z","msg":"記者林玉生／台北報導<br />\n<br />\n戴著黑框眼鏡，常飾演肌肉西裝上班族的「沖修斗」，是一名標準的日系同志天菜，今天40歲的他，平時喜愛吃牛排，下班喝啤酒，自在生活，因為娛樂公司片商有一個男演員「五十嵐裕也」，是他本身非常喜歡的型，想和他一起出演，所以就去面試了。沒想到錄取後，真的實現願望，與五十嵐裕也合作了幾部作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/91307677_3681650925238978_3870986356675051520_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=SkcYzH2TRzMAX_EWiND&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg2-1.fna&amp;oh=f2016ec22aa498b7f334596d1a1515fe&amp;oe=5FB0B88B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F91307677_3681650925238978_3870986356675051520_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DSkcYzH2TRzMAX_EWiND%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg2-1.fna%26oh%3Df2016ec22aa498b7f334596d1a1515fe%26oe%3D5FB0B88B&h=a1754733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖／沖修斗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/91440171_3681651468572257_2311163610405011456_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=zMH8xVMRJoUAX8yxnEZ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg2-1.fna&amp;oh=ef8af984b6e73578eff1440acdcef613&amp;oe=5FB1D086\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F91440171_3681651468572257_2311163610405011456_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DzMH8xVMRJoUAX8yxnEZ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg2-1.fna%26oh%3Def8af984b6e73578eff1440acdcef613%26oe%3D5FB1D086&h=5324c660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖／沖修斗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p403x403/91395475_3681655608571843_8497188913591353344_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=Yc2J5gvJB0MAX_Ccuzm&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg2-1.fna&amp;tp=6&amp;oh=3da62b611dd1a46ac436273bcf41c2d0&amp;oe=5FB062C8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp403x403%2F91395475_3681655608571843_8497188913591353344_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DYc2J5gvJB0MAX_Ccuzm%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg2-1.fna%26tp%3D6%26oh%3D3da62b611dd1a46ac436273bcf41c2d0%26oe%3D5FB062C8&h=fe197c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖／五十嵐裕也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p403x403/91544288_3681656331905104_7721420732198027264_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=xe9vy1fSGWcAX94N-RL&amp;_nc_oc=AQnsY7ai2ldJJhLW3Ym_s2HFdgEYdb3fQbmP-WKfF3p9uF2g7MvGhP6tSnd8Er87sHk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg2-1.fna&amp;tp=6&amp;oh=af1fc69db603a4c497ed95e99c2ac455&amp;oe=5FB2FEBF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp403x403%2F91544288_3681656331905104_7721420732198027264_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3Dxe9vy1fSGWcAX94N-RL%26_nc_oc%3DAQnsY7ai2ldJJhLW3Ym_s2HFdgEYdb3fQbmP-WKfF3p9uF2g7MvGhP6tSnd8Er87sHk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg2-1.fna%26tp%3D6%26oh%3Daf1fc69db603a4c497ed95e99c2ac455%26oe%3D5FB2FEBF&h=942fc38e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖／五十嵐裕也<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n「同志天菜」GV男優沖修斗 自爆入行原因：為了和欣賞的他共演<br />\n<br />\n日本成人產業發展多年，除了男女情愛動作片，也有專屬於同志的男男或女女類型，GV（Gay Video）演出的男優受歡迎程度不輸AV女優，其中有位GV男優「沖修斗」，以下垂的眼角、性感的鬍渣，與結實身材成為粉絲眼中「同志天菜」，而他透露入行契機，竟是想和欣賞的GV男優共演，「如果我進了這行，應該就有機會實現願望了吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20200331181338-b79454e013b87b212aa88fbc51cc9324-desktop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20200331181338-b79454e013b87b212aa88fbc51cc9324-desktop.jpg&h=5a83a7cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沖修斗在作品裡常以西裝造型現身，有「西裝哥」的別稱。（左圖翻攝自沖修斗IG，右圖網路圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年已經40歲的沖修斗入行約4年多，拍攝了近20部作品，他曾在訪問時談起入行經過，由於看GV時發現有欣賞的GV男優，讓他產生了「不如我也去拍片？」的想法。沖修斗帶著簡單的自我介紹與照片就到經紀公司面試，「沖修斗」這個藝名是他與工作人員想出來的，每次拍攝大概花費2到3小時，一部片可以收到日幣5萬元酬勞（約合新台幣1萬4,000元）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20200331181351-3b80e816010fe04d86d51c899b96ac09-desktop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20200331181351-3b80e816010fe04d86d51c899b96ac09-desktop.jpg&h=bd3c0664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五十嵐裕也就是讓沖修斗動心入行拍GV的「動機」。（網路圖片）<br />\n<br />\n讓沖修斗鼓起勇氣踏入GV這一行的是男優五十嵐裕也，他如願與對方共演了幾次，也獲得不少粉絲稱讚。不少GV男優都會往GOGOBOY（在同志夜店表演的舞者）發展，沖修斗卻謙稱自己身材不夠好，未將拍攝GV當作正職的他，平常也只是普通的上班族，過著朝九晚五的日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20200331181325-de725b11be091a58e28488dec98d9e60-desktop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20200331181325-de725b11be091a58e28488dec98d9e60-desktop.jpg&h=3e2de9d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沖修斗身上這件T恤是朋友從台灣買回去的伴手禮。（翻攝自沖修斗IG）<br />\n<br />\n喜歡用IG記錄生活點滴，沖修斗最新的IG更新竟與台灣有關，他穿著橘色無袖T恤自拍，寫到「穿上竹君很久前送的台灣伴手禮，無論怎樣調整，ㄋㄞㄋㄞ一直跑出來，不曉得該怎樣穿它了。」粉絲留言一連串愛心，瘋狂稱讚他自拍超帥，還有不少人留言「老公你最帥」「好希望在台灣見到你」。<br />\n<br />\n沖修斗 IG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/shuto.mukouzune/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fshuto.mukouzune%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=a211c1dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/shuto.mukouzune/</a><br />\n五十嵐裕也 IG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hiroya_nt/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhiroya_nt%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=513fb744\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hiroya_nt/</a>"},{"pid":"aa528c86c55cd71df2ded00e169652078ceac2dc","tid":2248513,"uid":136738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:54:35.000Z","msg":"幾正"},{"pid":"3a8438d9bfc3b5d080c17a6d6a2dc97715114c39","tid":2248513,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:38:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"339a7933b03dedc8530606e081cf24fc92a3ac87","tid":2248513,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"gay"},{"pid":"91b5c76475957d1b131d060ede44395139000a73","tid":2248513,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#jable#l"},{"pid":"9361fcba83e697fde8304b73e48877435cebc535","tid":2248513,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6faf521e3e00e7c4d4964ce8af5baf602836c48","tid":2248513,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"點解我會入左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b3a1bca08d4fb9d67fabcade7440391378db84","tid":2248513,"uid":3189,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b6faf521e3e00e7c4d4964ce8af5baf602836c48","tid":2248513,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"點解我會入左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"rep